name: Outdoor Gallery Series Presents: Obscured 009 in the Void
description: DESCRIPTION The digital painting, "Obscured 009" is resting upon a metallic cube which is built on a platform of sentient video feedback waves. Nestled into purple terrain that willed itself from the void, we find the exhibition tucked away. Intelligent orbs surround and hover above the platform, accompanying the painting. The orbs offer their companionship as it can be eons inbetween visitors. mp4. 1280x1280 pixels.
